  "3129930": {
    "name": "银河灰暗角落",
    "steam_appid": 3129930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/7fee69019228815c5148ebf382749638.poster.avif?t=1772265844\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/7fee69019228815c5148ebf382749638.webm?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/7fee69019228815c5148ebf382749638.mp4?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《银河灰暗角落》是一款<strong>太空舰队策略 Rogue-lite</strong>。你是公司派遣的外勤调查员，在银河文明的“灰暗角落”接单求生： <strong>交涉、威胁、开战或撤离</strong>——每一次选择，都在收益与风险之间写下你的结算单。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你将获得的体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>带舰队出勤接单 → 交涉/战斗/抉择 → 打捞回收 → 模块改装与基地休整 → 下一趟出勤继续赌更大的收益。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/0153fcde25312f2913bdce95b0c46927.avif?t=1772265844\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是单船独舞，而是<strong>舰队部署与战术选择</strong>。 你可以让 AI 托管作战，也可以手动点控集火与走位，用更精细的指挥争取优势：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>编队与站位</strong>决定火力覆盖与生存空间</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>目标选择与集火</strong>影响击破节奏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>该打就打、该撤就撤</strong>，活着回去才有下一趟出勤</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/3324431f927780fcba35bc5926d70926.poster.avif?t=1772265844\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/3324431f927780fcba35bc5926d70926.webm?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/3324431f927780fcba35bc5926d70926.mp4?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/0b088a6e47ae7ee10d0041ed6d6159d4.poster.avif?t=1772265844\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/0b088a6e47ae7ee10d0041ed6d6159d4.webm?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/0b088a6e47ae7ee10d0041ed6d6159d4.mp4?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/a533afed99d5c15bb147edca59138843.avif?t=1772265844\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次出勤都是一次“赌局”：路线、战斗与事件会带来不同的收益与代价。 你要做的不只是赢，还要算清楚<strong>成本、损耗与回收价值</strong>——因为打捞回来的东西，才是你滚起战力的起点。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>模块改装</strong>：捡到更好的模块，立刻替换，战力提升直观可感</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>路线对赌</strong>：稳妥路线更安全，高风险路线可能产出更稀有的模块与奖励</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>撤退止损</strong>：打不过就撤并不可耻，但损耗与扣款会写进结算（这是策略的一部分）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/da5f169637555bec8e202032e2577682.poster.avif?t=1772265844\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/da5f169637555bec8e202032e2577682.webm?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/da5f169637555bec8e202032e2577682.mp4?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/dcdc838e256d5bd687de5b7e259257b5.avif?t=1772265844\" width=616 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >银河的光鲜属于“文明”，灰暗留给“外勤”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你会在任务中遇到荒诞离奇的事件与势力纠葛，黑色幽默贯穿对话与制度：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时候你以为按下了“暂停”，其实只是又多了一笔流程和代价</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时候你打赢了战斗，却在结算里发现收益先被公司抽走 在这里，最真实的敌人不止炮火，还有规则。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/d69f1a8bd30625588636cef0a932d4e0.poster.avif?t=1772265844\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/d69f1a8bd30625588636cef0a932d4e0.webm?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129930/extras/d69f1a8bd30625588636cef0a932d4e0.mp4?t=1772265844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>了解开发进度和游戏详情、聊天、问题反馈、意向合作 ↓ </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>QQ交流群：816338211   </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>邮箱：feedback@brickup.cn</i> </p>",
